title: Wary Business Operator
description: As a facchino who operates two of the Consiglio's properties (Contract Stall and Small Warehouse), our relationship is characterized by professional necessity rather than trust. Despite the significant business connection indicated by our high relationship strength score (344.89), the negative trust score (-50.63) reveals underlying tension, likely stemming from issues such as zero wages at my warehouse and the Consiglio's zero rent policy for their properties I operate.
